    'about.h2':'Free online tools that run in your browser — no install',
    'about.body':'<p>gemini2k tools is a free collection of online utilities you can use right in your browser, with no sign-up or installation. It covers character counting, unit and coordinate conversion, QR and password generation, image and PDF processing, developer tools like JSON and regex, and even professional GIS tools such as coordinate-system conversion and spatial operations — all in one place.</p><p>Every calculation runs entirely inside your browser. The text you type or the files you upload are never sent to or stored on our servers, so you can work with sensitive documents with peace of mind.</p><h3>Key features</h3><ul><li><strong>No install</strong> — works instantly on desktop and mobile, just a browser</li><li><strong>Privacy first</strong> — input data is processed on your device, never uploaded</li><li><strong>Free & multilingual</strong> — Korean / English / 中文 / 日本語</li></ul><h3>What you can do</h3><ul><li><strong>Text</strong> — character counter, text cleanup (case, dedupe, sort)</li><li><strong>Calc & convert</strong> — age/D-day, unit, color, lunar-solar</li><li><strong>Generators</strong> — QR codes, strong passwords, lottery numbers</li><li><strong>Image & PDF</strong> — image compress/resize, PDF merge/split/compress, image→PDF</li><li><strong>Developer</strong> — JSON formatter/validator, regex tester, Markdown editor, Base64</li><li><strong>GIS & maps</strong> — coordinate conversion, distance/area on a web map, WKT/GeoJSON conversion, spatial ops, location de-identification</li><li><strong>Privacy</strong> — PII detection/masking, re-identification risk assessment</li></ul><h3>FAQ</h3><p><strong>Q. Is my input stored on a server?</strong><br/>No. Everything is processed in your browser; input data is never sent or stored.</p><p><strong>Q. Do I need to sign up or log in?</strong><br/>No. Just open the page and start using it.</p><p><strong>Q. Is it free?</strong><br/>All tools are free. Ads may be shown to support the site.</p><p class="muted">For details on cookies and ads, see our <a href="privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>',
